query:
SELECT h.id, h.name as hotel_name, d.name as doc_name, d.fileUrl 
FROM hotels h 
LEFT JOIN documents d ON (d.category='other' OR d.category='booking') 
  AND d.fileUrl LIKE '%.jpg%' OR d.fileUrl LIKE '%.jpeg%' OR d.fileUrl LIKE '%.png%' OR d.fileUrl LIKE '%.webp%'
ORDER BY h.id;
